ty may provide a\nuseful way to quantify the change in a network's community structure.\n","versions":[{"version":"v1","created":"Tue, 31 May 2011 22:16:31 GMT"},{"version":"v2","created":"Wed, 15 Jun 2011 21:00:09 GMT"},{"version":"v3","created":"Tue, 2 Aug 2011 14:57:14 GMT"}],"update_date":"2011-08-03"}
